race.comment: MR. THOMAS (1) missed the frame last time at The Meadows but the start prior rocketed around 500m at Bendigo in 28.09. Rates a top chance if runs up to time two back. HIGHLY CONNECTED (3) turned in a plain effort last time when seventh at Sandown over 515m behind Barefoot Zulu (29.92) in a Special conditions race. Form from his last run is proving strong. Warrants plenty of respect. SPRITELY SIAN (4) is a talented type who has been in the money at the last four starts, the latest finishing second (25.91) at this track. Form here sound including two wins. Looks suited and expected to run well. BANDIT DARYL (2) is one to consider despite coming off a brief layoff. Something for the Multiples: MR. THOMAS (1)
